{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第20章摘要：本章共5个段落，148条对话。出场人物：小马、常无意、朱五太爷、卜战、张聋子、无舌童子、年轻人、朱云、蓝兰、宋三、温良玉、小琳、老皮、太阳使者。主要情节：小马发现朱五太爷已死，朱云身份揭晓，蓝兰讲述往事，太阳使者威胁，老皮牺牲，朱云承诺改革狼山，小琳离开小马。主题：友情、牺牲、宽恕、新生。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"别人敢过去，我为什么不敢？难道我真是条被人牵着拉磨的驴子？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "———他天生就有双锐眼，而且久经训练，就在这道珠帘被\"站住\"那两个喝声振动时，发现了这秘密。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "——\"站\"字是开口音，可是说出这个字的人，嘴却没有动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马忍不住问：\"你究竟是谁？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"我知道你一定不姓蓝，更不会叫蓝寄云。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的目光闪动，忽然问：\"你是不是姓朱？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马突然明白：\"难道你是他的…他的儿子？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只听一个人在帘外轻轻道：\"不错，他就是朱五太爷的独生子朱云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"你和朱五太爷已是多年的伙伴？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"很多很多年了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"但是你刚才并没有认出朱云就是他的独生子。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"朱云十三岁时就已离开狼山，这十年都没有回来过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"'无论对任何人来说，十年间的变化都太大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"他为什么要走，为什么不回来？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"他天生就是练武的奇才，十三岁时，就认为自己的武功己不在他父亲之下，就想到外面去闯他自己的天下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"可是他父亲不肯让他走。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"一个人晚年得子，当然舍不得让自己的独生子离开自己的身边。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"所以朱云就自己偷偷溜走了？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"他是有个志气的孩子，而且脾气也和他父亲同样固执，如果决定了一件事，谁都没法子让他改变。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他叹息着，又道：\"这十年来，虽然没有人知道他在哪里，可是我和他父亲都知道，以他的脾气，在外面一定吃了不少苦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马转向蓝兰：\"这十年来他在干什么，也许只有你最清楚。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰并不否认：\"他虽然吃了不少苦，也练成了不少武功绝技，为了要学别人的功夫，什么事他都可以做得出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"可是他忽然厌倦了，他忽然发现一个人就算能练成天下无敌的功夫，有时反而会觉得更空虚寂寞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她的神情黯然，慢慢地接着道：\"因为他没有家人的关怀，也没有朋友，他的武功练得越高，心里反而越痛苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马凝视着蓝兰，道：\"你不关心他？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"我关心他，可是我也知道，他真正需要的安慰与关怀，绝不是我能给他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"是他的父亲？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰点点头。道：\"只有他的父亲，才是他这一生中真正唯一敬爱的人，可是他的脾气实在太倔强，非但死也不肯承认这一点，而且总觉得自己是溜出来的，已没有脸再回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：'我们都曾经下山去找过他。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"那几年他还未体会到亲情的可贵，所以一直避不见面，等他想回来的时候，已经听不见你们的消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"他救过我们蓝家一家人的性命，我当然不能看着他受苦，所以我就偷偷地替他写了很多封信，千方百计托人带到狼山上来，希望朱五太爷能派人下山去接他的儿子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"我们为什么都不知道这回事？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰叹息道：\"那也许只因为我所托非人，使得这些信都落入一个恶贼的手里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她接着又道：\"可是当时我们都没有想到这一点，因为我的信发出不久，狼山上就有人带来了朱五太爷的回音。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"什么回音？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道，\"那个人叫宋三，看样子很诚恳，自称是朱五太爷的亲信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"我从未听说过这个人。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"他这姓名当然是假的，只可惜我们以后永远都不会知道他究竟是谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战道：\"为什么？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"因为现在他连尸骨都已腐烂。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她又补充着道：\"他送来的是个密封的蜡丸，一定要朱云亲手副开，因为蜡丸中藏着的是朱五太爷给他儿子的密函，绝不能让第三者看见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"想不到蜡丸中，却藏着是一股毒烟和三枚毒针。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马抢着问道：\"朱云中了他的暗算？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰苦笑道：\"有谁能想得到亲父亲会暗算自己的儿子？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"宋三呢？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"宋三来的时候，已经中了剧毒，他刚想逃走时，毒性就已发作，不到片刻间，连骨带肉都已腐烂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马握紧拳头，道：\"好狠的人，好毒辣的手段。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"可是虎毒不食子，那时我们已想到，叫宋三送信来的，一定另有其人，他不愿让朱五太爷父子重逢，因为他知道朱云一回去，必将继承朱五太爷的霸业。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她叹息着道：\"我们同时还想到了另外更可怕的一点。\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"哪一点？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"这个人既然敢这么样做，朱五太爷纵然没有死，也必定病在垂危。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战立刻同意，恨恨道：\"朱五太爷惊才绝世，他若平安无恙，这个人就算有天大的胆子，也绝不敢这么样做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"父子关心，出于天性，到了这时候，朱云也不能再固执了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她又叹了口气，道：\"可是我们也想到了，这个人既然敢暗算朱五太爷的独生子，在狼山上一定已有了可以左右一切的势力。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜战替她补充，道：\"因为那时你们还不能确定他的死活，朱云纵然功力绝世，毒性毕竟没有完全消除，出手时多少总要受到些影响的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_zhan",
      "speaker_name": "卜战",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"可惜我们也不能再等下去，所以我们一定要另外想个万无一失的法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"所以你们想到了我。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰点头道：\"我们并不想欺骗你，只不过这件事实在太秘密，绝不能泄露一点消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马也叹了口气，点头道：\"其实我也并没有怪你，这本来就是我自己心甘情愿的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "常无意冷冷道：\"现在我只想知道一件事。\"",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"什么事？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "常无意道：\"主使这件阴谋的究竟是谁？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马没有回答，蓝兰和卜战也没有，可是他们心里都同时想到了一个人——\"狼君子\"温良玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"不管他逃到那里去，都逃不了的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我们就算要追，也绝不能走这条秘道！\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"为什么？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"以他的阴险和深沉，一定会在秘道中留下极厉害的埋伏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"卜战毕竟老谋深算，\"这一次我们绝不能再因为激动而误了大事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他又冲了出去，蓝兰在后面追着他问：\"你想去哪里？去干什么？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"去干掉一个人。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"谁？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"一个总是躲在面具后的人。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰的眼睛里发出光，又道：\"你认为他很可能就是温良玉？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"是的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"就是他？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"是的。\"小马很信心：\"除了温良玉之外，我想不出第二个人。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马冲出来，瞪着对岸的太阳使者：\"你居然还在这里？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "使者道：\"我为什么要走？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"因为你做的事。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"这些事你做得很成功，只可惜朱云还没有死，我也没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "使者道：\"他没有死，是他的运气；你没有死，是我的运气。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_yang_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"是你的运气？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "使者道：\"因为朱云不是你的朋友，小琳和老皮却是的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "使者道：\"而且你还有双拳头，还有个会用剑的朋友，朱云却已只剩下半条命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"你要我杀了他，换回小琳？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "使者道：\"这世上喜新厌旧的人并不少，也许你会为了蓝兰而牺牲小琳，只不过我相信你绝不是这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "使者道：\"我也可以保证，以你的拳头，和常无意的剑，已足够对付朱云。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你把我当朋友，我不能让你丢人。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"朋友。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"现在我才知道，无论多高深的武功，也比不上真正的友情。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先开口的是朱云：\"现在我也知道你才是个真正了不起的人，因为你信任朋友，朋友也信任你，因为你可以为朋友死，朋友也愿意为你死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱云道：\"谁都想不到老皮这么样是为了你，我也想不到，所以我不如你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他叹息，又道：\"我也知道我对不起你，可是我至少也可以为你做几件事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱云道：\"我可以保证，狼山上从此再也没有恶狼，也没有吃草的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说：\"谢谢你！\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她没有面对小马，只轻轻的说：\"我知道你在找我，也知道你为我做的事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"那么你——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小琳道：\"我对不起你。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lin",
      "speaker_name": "小琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马道：\"你用不着对我说这三个字。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小琳道：\"我一定要说，因为我已经永远没法子再跟你在一起，我们之间已经有了永远无法弥补的裂痕，在一起只有痛苦更深。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lin",
      "speaker_name": "小琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lin",
      "speaker_name": "小琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她在流泪，泪落如雨：\"所以你若真的对我还有一点儿好，就应该让我走。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰一直在看着他们，忽然问：\"这世上真有永远无法弥补的裂痕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "常无意道：\"没有。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他脸上还是全无表情：\"只要有真的情，不管多大的裂痕，都一定可以弥补。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓝兰道：\"这句话你是对谁说的？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "常无意道：\"那个象驴子一样笨的小马。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    }
